description:
Angels are such a silly idea that they count as evidence against Christianity. If god is omnipotent then he wouldn't need henchmen to do his dirty work. He could just do everything himself. Please don't respond with "Free will must exist because god doesn't want a bunch of robots worshipping him." This argument has nothing to do with the free will involved with worship. It instead has to do with the risk involved in hiring foot soldiers to work for him. The Bible says angels have a 33% chance of disobedience. There's no risk or cost for god to just do everything himself.

description:
